00:01:10,071 --> 00:01:13,017
是的 我们能 小妞...
Yes, we can, Freckles...

24
00:01:13,018 --> 00:01:15,088
因为是他让我们这样做的
'cause that's what he asked us to do.

25
00:01:15,089 --> 00:01:17,088
你想想  如果我们回去
I mean, think about it? We go back there,

