是时候了
Time to get up.

33
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,075
我们要把你转走
We're moving you.

34
00:01:52,005 --> 00:01:55,084
- 去哪里?   - 另外一个地方 Jack
- Moving me where?   - Someplace else, Jack.

35
