Let me ask you something.

84
00:07:26,084 --> 00:07:29,041
你冒着生命危险
You risk your neck to cut them loose,

85
00:07:29,042 --> 00:07:31,067
帮他们逃走...
and they run away and don't ever look back...

86
00:07:31,068 --> 00:07:34,051
谢谢你给我的三明治
Thanks for the sandwich.

87
00:07:43,006 --> 00:07:45,093
真没想到我又回来了
Never thought I'd be glad to get back to this rock again.

88
00:07:45,094 --> 00:07:47,031
你在干吗?
What are you doing?

89
00:07:47,032 --> 00:07:49,027
你说在干吗  我们要上岸啊!
What's it look like? I'm heading into shore.

90
00:07:49,099 --> 00:07:51,053
如果我们沿着海岸继续划 可以划到我们的营地
If we just keep going, we can circle round.

91
00:07:51,053 --> 00:07:54,040
我们可以告诉 Locke 和 Sayid 发生了什么
Sooner or later we'll get to camp and tell Locke and Sayid what happened.

92
00:07:54,041 --> 00:07:55,019
我们会的是吗?
Oh, we will?

93
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:59,004
你有地图吗 麦哲伦小妞?
You got a map you ain't showing me, Magellan?

94
00:07:59,046 --> 00:08:01,020
我们没有水没有食物
We got no food, no water,

95
00:08:01,021 --> 00:08:03,020
