102
00:08:38,087 --> 00:08:41,032
你什么时候醒的?
When the hell did you wake up?

103
00:08:41,033 --> 00:08:45,053
你们不该吵架 因为你们幸运的活了下来
You shouldn't fight because you're lucky to be alive.

104
00:08:45,054 --> 00:08:49,075
我想他说到点子上了
Golly! I think he's got a point!

105
00:08:51,042 --> 00:08:54,050
你们住在那座岛上吗?
That island we were on... Is that where your people live?

106
00:08:54,051 --> 00:08:58,080
- 只是用来工作  - 什么工作?
- Just where we work.  - Work on what?

107
00:08:58,081 --> 00:09:00,017
一些工程
Projects.

108
00:09:00,018 --> 00:09:03,072
就像 "把孩子从木伐上偷走" 的工程?
Oh, sure, like the "steal the kid off the raft" project?

109
00:09:03,073 --> 00:09:05,018
干的真是出色
That was a humdinger.

110
00:09:05,019 --> 00:09:08,010
你们不是住在那座岛上的?
So you don't actually live on that island?

111
00:09:08,077 --> 00:09:10,039
你住在这里...
Do you live here...

112
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:12,039
这座岛上吗?
on this island?

113
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:14,082
是的 女士
Yes, ma'am.

114
00:09:17,032 --> 00:09:20,078
那你们为什么要抓那些人...
And what did you do with the people that you took...

115
00:09:20,079 --> 00:09:21,099
和孩子们?
the kids?

116
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,061
我们要给他们更好的生活
We give them a better life.

117
00:09:23,062 --> 00:09:25,087
相对什么?
Better than what?

118
00:09:25,092 --> 00:09:28,029
相对你们的生活
Better than yours.

119
00:09:35,009 --> 00:09:38,021
今晚不会有月亮了
There's not gonna be any moon tonight.

120
00:09:38,022 --> 00:09:40,009
将是一片黑暗
It'll be dark.

121
