你还看不见 但...
You can't see it yet,

124
00:09:47,015 --> 00:09:51,022
那个是"ursa theodorus"...
but right there will be "Ursa Theodorus"...

125
00:09:51,023 --> 00:09:53,010
泰迪熊
the teddy bear.

126
00:09:53,011 --> 00:09:56,070
- 你还有后院?  - 是的
- You have backyards?  -Yeah.

127
00:09:58,066 --> 00:10:00,099
那听起来真诱人
Well, ain't that quaint?

128
00:10:05,029 --> 00:10:07,017
警报
Warning!

129
00:10:12,013 --> 00:10:13,092
警报
Warning!

130
