他们让我检查 Ben
They let me out to examine Ben.

132
00:10:35,082 --> 00:10:38,040
他的器官活动很底 还有高烧
His vitals are low, and he has a fever.

133
00:10:38,041 --> 00:10:40,065
这是我10分钟前拍的
I took this about ten minutes ago.

134
00:10:40,066 --> 00:10:43,012
是他的缝针
It's of his stitches.

135
00:10:44,062 --> 00:10:47,049
他们被感染了?
They're infected, aren't they?

136
00:10:47,050 --> 00:10:48,036
是的
Yes.

137
00:10:48,037 --> 00:10:50,087
你能来看看他吗?
Will you come look at them?

138
00:10:50,088 --> 00:10:51,087
不行
No.

139
00:10:51,088 --> 00:10:53,009
- Jack - 不行
- Jack.  -No.

140
00:10:53,010 --> 00:10:55,075
你不必为他们... 或他这么做
I'm not asking you for them... or him.

141
00:10:55,076 --> 00:10:59,093
就算是为了我
I'm asking you as a personal favor to me.

142
00:11:01,055 --> 00:11:04,092
你想让我再帮他一次?
You... want me to help him again?

143
00:11:04,093 --> 00:11:06,051
是的
Yes.

144
00:11:06,052 --> 00:11:08,093
你确定吗 Juliet?
Are you sure about that, Juliet?

145
00:11:08,094 --> 00:11:11,055
是的 我很确定
Yes... I'm sure.

146
00:11:11,056 --> 00:11:15,027
这是因为他能让你回家吗?
And this is because he said that he would let you go home?

147
00:11:15,028 --> 00:11:16,099
不是的
No.

148
00:11:18,053 --> 00:11:20,028
不 我...
No, I...

149
00:11:22,066 --> 00:11:25,044
因为我遇到麻烦了
It's because I'm in trouble.

150
00:11:25,045 --> 00:11:27,095
- 麻烦? 为了...  - 我杀了个人
- Trouble? For...  - I just killed someone.

151
00:11:27,096 --> 00:11:30,032
所以他们把我关起来了
That's why they put me in your room.

152
00:11:30,033 --> 00:11:32,038
你杀了谁?
Who?

153
00:11:34,075 --> 00:11:36,096
这很复杂
It's complicated.

154
00:11:38,026 --> 00:11:41,083
让我直接和你说吧
Well, then, let me simplify it for you.

155
00:11:41,084 --> 00:11:44,051
我不会帮他的...
I'm not gonna help him...

156
00:11:45,093 --> 00:11:49,006
我也不会帮你
and I'm not gonna help you.

157
00:12:11,025 --> 00:12:15,079
今日特别泰国菜 你尝尝
Special Thai dish for you. You try.

158
00:12:26,072 --> 00:12:30,072
非常勇敢!
Very brave, very brave.

159
00:12:32,056 --> 00:12:34,047
我哥哥喜欢你
My brother likes you.

160
00:12:34,048 --> 00:12:37,081
我是一个受欢迎的人
Well, I'm a very likeable guy.

161
00:12:40,023 --> 00:12:42,065
Jack...

162
00:12:42,078 --> 00:12:44,094
问你个问题
tell me something.

163
00:12:44,095 --> 00:12:46,052
说吧
Shoot.

164
00:12:46,053 --> 00:12:50,066
为什么你不懂怎么放风筝?
Why is it you don't know how to fly a kite?

165
00:12:51,012 --> 00:12:54,074
- 我从没学过  - 那真可惜
- Just never learned, I guess.  - That's very sad.

166
00:12:54,075 --> 00:12:57,066
我爸工作很忙
Well, my dad worked a lot.

167
00:12:57,067 --> 00:13:01,016
而且他也不是那种会喜欢放风筝的人
He wasn't exactly the kite-flying type, anyway.

168
00:13:01,017 --> 00:13:02,083
- 我的意思是 我们  - Jack
- I mean, we never really...  -Jack

169
00:13:02,084 --> 00:13:07,014
- 怎么了?  - 我对你父亲不感兴趣
- Yeah?  - I have no interest in your father.

170
00:13:07,018 --> 00:13:10,084
好吧 我也厌倦了总是说起他
Well, that's a relief,because I'm pretty tired of talking about him.

171
00:13:10,085 --> 00:13:13,085
有些事可以放在心里
Some things are personal.

172
00:13:19,098 --> 00:13:25,024
