So you're in Phuket to... "find yourself"?

173
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:29,078
- 为什么这么说?  - 你是个美国人
- Why would you say that?  - You're an American.

174
00:13:49,009 --> 00:13:50,038
我有...
I have...

175
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:52,030
一个天赋
a gift.

176
00:13:52,031 --> 00:13:55,098
那一定很值得期待
Must be one hell of a gift.

177
00:14:22,054 --> 00:14:25,041
我在读你纹身上的字
I was just reading your tattoos.

178
00:14:25,042 --> 00:14:28,017
"五" 和周围的星星都很漂亮
The "five" and the stars are very cute,

179
00:14:28,018 --> 00:14:31,089
