But the Chinese I find...

180
00:14:33,006 --> 00:14:35,021
有点讽刺
a bit ironic.

181
00:14:35,022 --> 00:14:39,019
- 什么讽刺?  - 它所表达的
- You find what ironic?  - What it says.

182
00:14:40,002 --> 00:14:43,052
你知道它表示什么?
You do know what it says?

183
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:47,060
是的 我知道
Yeah, I know what it says.

184
00:14:47,061 --> 00:14:49,027
你确定吗?
Are you sure?

185
00:14:49,028 --> 00:14:51,098
中文是一种很复杂的语言
Chinese is a very complicated language.

186
00:14:51,099 --> 00:14:55,048
我们往往会不能完全理解它的意思
It's fairly common for some things to get lost in translation.

187
00:14:55,049 --> 00:15:01,000
- 我知道它表示什么  - 那好吧
- I know what it says.  - All right, then.

188
00:15:02,079 --> 00:15:04,054
Jack...

189
00:15:06,021 --> 00:15:09,017
我的名字叫 Isabel
My name is Isabel.

190
00:15:09,076 --> 00:15:12,050
如果你跟我来
If you'll come with me,

191
00:15:12,051 --> 00:15:17,035
我要问你几个问题
