He has, however, ordered her to be marked.

395
00:33:55,080 --> 00:33:58,009
你去哪儿?
Hey, where you going?

396
00:34:10,069 --> 00:34:13,035
我认识你
Hey, I know you.

397
00:34:13,077 --> 00:34:16,052
我是 Achara 的朋友 从...
I'm Achara's friend from...

398
00:34:16,053 --> 00:34:20,019
我来过你的餐馆
Chet's,from the restaurant.

399
00:34:24,003 --> 00:34:26,049
放开我 兄弟
Let go of me, man.

400
00:34:49,052 --> 00:34:51,018
滚出我们的海滩!
You will get off our beach!

401
00:34:51,019 --> 00:34:52,089
然后滚出这个国家!
You leave this country!

402
00:34:52,090 --> 00:34:55,077
你明白吗?!
Do you understand me?

403
00:35:58,034 --> 00:36:01,021
听说你只喜欢烤的
I heard you only liked them grilled.

404
00:36:03,026 --> 00:36:07,047
我也想念这个牙签了
I missed the toothpicks, too.

405
00:36:15,056 --> 00:36:17,064
- 让我看看  - Jack...
- Let me see.  - Jack...

406
00:36:17,065 --> 00:36:21,032
他们给你做记号 让我看看
They marked you. Let me see it.

407
00:36:41,000 --> 00:36:44,000
折一片芦荟给我...
Break a branch off that aloe plant over there...

408
00:36:44,001 --> 00:36:45,079
- 没关系的 Jack   - 求你了
- It's ok, Jack.  - Please.

409
00:36:45,080 --> 00:36:48,022
求你了
Please do it.

410
00:37:03,023 --> 00:37:05,019
好了 转过身
All right, turn around.

411
00:37:27,084 --> 00:37:30,054
为什么帮我?
Why did you help me?

412
00:37:30,055 --> 00:37:33,042
他告诉你会让你回家
He told you he was gonna let you go home.

413
00:37:33,043 --> 00:37:36,022
他也许诺我同样的事
He told me the same thing.

414
00:37:36,035 --> 00:37:39,030
我们要保证他说到做到
We're gonna make sure he keeps his word.

415
00:37:39,031 --> 00:37:41,089
我们怎么做?
And how are we going to do that?

416
00:37:41,090 --> 00:37:44,011
一起面对
Together.

417
00:37:55,091 --> 00:38:01,066
过几分钟他们都会来找你
They'll be coming for you in a few minutes... All of them.

418
00:38:01,067 --> 00:38:03,058
你的朋友知道我们在哪儿
Your friends know where we are,

419
00:38:03,059 --> 00:38:07,062
所以我们要回去我们住的地方
so we have to leave this island to go back to where we live.

420
00:38:07,063 --> 00:38:10,026
去哪儿?
Go where?

421
00:38:10,055 --> 00:38:13,068
Ben 叫它"家园"
Well, Ben calls it "home."

422
00:38:18,039 --> 00:38:22,052
- Karl 在哪里?   - 我让他走了
- Where's Karl?  -I let him go.

423
00:38:22,094 --> 00:38:25,051
- 什么?   - 我让他走了
- You what?  - I let him go.

424
00:38:25,052 --> 00:38:27,060
他能带我们去他们住的地方
He could have led us back to where they live.

425
00:38:27,061 --> 00:38:30,056
你以为我放了他 是因为我很敏感吗?
What, you think I cut him loose 'cause I'm so damn sensitive?

426
00:38:30,057 --> 00:38:32,056
那孩子是靶子
The kid's a target.

427
00:38:32,057 --> 00:38:36,007
Ben 不会放弃找到他 直到...
Ben ain't never gonna stop looking for him, so as long...

428
00:38:36,008 --> 00:38:40,082
Ben 只想让他远离他女儿
All Ben wants is that kid as far from his daughter as possible.

429
00:38:40,083 --> 00:38:43,054
我们回营地吧
Let's get back to camp.

430
00:38:47,080 --> 00:38:50,008
你来不来啊?
Are you coming or not?

431
00:38:50,009 --> 00:38:54,034
我是和你一起走 还是跟在你后面比较好?
Should I walk beside you or ten paces behind you?

432
00:38:54,039 --> 00:38:57,092
难道你就不觉得很自私么?
You're so good at telling me what to do, I can't think for myself anymore.

433
00:38:57,093 --> 00:39:00,047
别因为你自己有罪恶感 就把这些盖到我头上
Don't take it out on me 'cause you feel guilty.

434
00:39:00,048 --> 00:39:02,018
- 我没感到罪恶  - 才怪!
- I don't feel guilty.  - The hell you don't!

435
00:39:02,019 --> 00:39:04,068
我们必须留下Jack  我没有选择...
We had to leave Jack behind. I didn't have a choice...

436
00:39:04,069 --> 00:39:08,015
我不是说这个
I'm not talking about leaving Jack behind.

437
00:39:11,074 --> 00:39:16,087
我是说你我的事
I'm talking about you and me.

438
00:39:22,092 --> 00:39:26,095
你这么做是因为 你知道我死定了...
I know you did it 'cause you thought I was a dead man...

439
00:39:26,096 --> 00:39:31,042
不要因为医生还留在那里  而埋怨自己
so don't beat yourself up 'cause the doc's left behind.

440
00:39:33,038 --> 00:39:36,017
我没有埋怨自己
I'm not beating myself up.

441
00:39:36,018 --> 00:39:38,064
当然
'Course you're not.

442
00:39:43,085 --> 00:39:48,002
现在我们可以走了吗?
So now that we got that out of the way, let's go.

443
00:40:12,088 --> 00:40:18,000
"他与我们共同前进，但却不是我们的一员"
"He walks amongst us, but he is not one of us."

444
00:40:18,001 --> 00:40:22,035
这就是你纹身的意义
Your tattoos...That's what they say.

445
00:40:26,035 --> 00:40:28,060
这是他们说的
That's what they say.

446
